    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Lucius Aurelius Su<lb break="no" n="2"/>rus <expan><abbr>bul</abbr><ex>euta</ex></expan> civitatis IVS <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elium</ex></expan> Surum <expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>eranum</ex></expan> ex <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>signif</abbr><ex>ero</ex></expan> patrem et <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audiam</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Gaillam matrem et <lb n="6"/>Domitiam Valentiam <lb n="7"/>coniugem secum ita <lb n="8"/>haec memoriae con<lb break="no" n="9"/>silio suo usus <lb n="10"/>de suo dignatus est
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nicht mehr auffindbar. Inschriftfeld in Form einer mit Weinranken geschmückten Tafel (45 x 40 cm). (B): ILBulg: Z. 4: [C]l(audiam); Boyadzhiev: Z. 4: [C]laudiam; Z. 10: dignatu[s].</p>
            </div>
